            "content": "Levels, encounters, item placements, and environmental hazards balanced so each run feels demanding but fair. The game has to be hard for the right reasons, not the cheap ones.",
            "variant": "body",
            "align": "left",
            "color": "foreground",
            "transform": "none"
          }
        }
